BT /F3 8.8 Tf 54 738.00 Td (8. Verify login, search, dashboard, reports, add/edit.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.8 Tf 54 726.00 Td (9. Preserve damaged dump until investigation is complete.) Tj ET
endstream
